reviews.review_text:
My future wife's first show This recording has good dynamic range and separation. 
I was there with my future wife-to-be, introducing her to the Dead for the first time. She said the music was "pretty". She was blown away by people doing blow right in front of us. I learned years later 4that she lied when she said she liked the band. She had her eyes on me and didn't want to lose me over something like musical tastes. Alas, she passed 4 years ago, after 35 years of marriage.

Scott Wiseman for the win I have been noticing Taper Scott Wiseman has been recently uploading his recordings from nearly every year. Im finding them everywhere here on Archive. They are consistently impressive. This one is no exception. Thank you Scott for sharing your work.
